i |first2=Maariv |last2=Hashavua |agency=Reuters |work=[[Jerusalem Post]] |date=27 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030033929/http://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Report-ISIS-Rambo-killed-in-battle-south-of-Mosul-471023 |archivedate=30 October 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n| units1      = ''See [[Order of battle for the Battle of Mosul (2016\u201317)#Anti-ISIL forces|anti-ISIL forces order of battle]]''\n| units2      = ''See [[Order of battle for the Battle of Mosul (2016\u201317)#Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant|ISIL order of battle]]''\n| strength1   = '''Total:''' 108,500\u2013114,000 fighters<ref name=\"Mosul battle forces\" />\n* {{flagicon|Iraq}} 54,000\u201360,000 ISF troops<ref name=\"cnn1017\">{{cite news |last1=Walsh |first1=Nick Paton |last2=Blau |first2=Max |last3=Park |first3=Madison |last4=McLaughlin |first4=Eliott C. |title=Battle for Mosul: Iraqi forces inflict 'heavy losses' |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/17/middleeast/mosul-isis-operation-begins-iraq/index.html |publisher=[[CNN]] |date=17 October 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017071928/http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/17/middleeast/mosul-isis-operation-begins-iraq/index.html |archivedate=17 October 2016 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"ptv\" />\n* 14,000 paramilitary troops<ref name=\"cnn1017\" />\n* {{flagicon|Kurdistan}} 40,000 Peshmerga troops<ref name=\"cnn1017\" />\n'''Support:'''<br />{{flagicon image|Seal of Combined Joint Task Force \u2013 Operation Inherent Resolve.svg|size=25px|border=no}} 450 CJTF\u2013OIR advisers<ref name=\"offensive in Anbar\">{{cite web |url=http://www.thenational.ae/world/middle-east/iraq-launches-offensive-on-isil-in-anbar-province |title=Iraq launches offensive on ISIL in Anbar province |publisher=The National |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106083734/http://www.thenational.ae/world/middle-east/iraq-launches-offensive-on-isil-in-anbar-province |archivedate=6 January 